Persons Must Have a Negative Polymerase Chain Reaction (Pcr) Test or Nucleic Acid Amplification Test (Naat) Taken Within 3 Days of Arrival In Grenada (Date of Sample Collection Must Be Within 3 Days of Arrival In Grenada) or a Negative Rapid Antigen Test Taken Within 1 Day Of Arrival In Grenada (Date of Sample Collection Must Be Within 1 Day of Arrival In Grenada). Photo via NOWGrenada.Grenada currently accepts fully vaccinated visitors only. There is NO quarantine on arrival. Please see entry process outlined below.